      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right owner? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little car that could make a great budget commuter, first project, or handy spare. It shows its age and has its quirks, but it\u2019s priced fairly and could be a smart buy for someone who wants simple, usable transport without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re after something cheap, straightforward, and worth a look, send me a message \u2014 happy to chat.",
