      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with stories in its sheet metal and plenty of life for the next owner with vision. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who wants affordable transportation, a hands-on project, or a dependable backup with personality. The look is seasoned, the vibe is unpretentious, and it offers a great opportunity to get into a vehicle with real potential without spending big. If you appreciate a car with grit, charm, and room to make it your own, this one is worth a look.",
